{"TopicId":51920,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Riddles","CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-05T03:12:01Z","PageNum":153,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T17:56:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EProbably very easy, but it\u0027s my first riddle, so be gentle \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOk, here goes:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EAs the supreme authority of this dimension,\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EI am the first and the last one of the lot\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EWhen the mood is solitary,\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EMy sword acompanies both of my selves.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EMy exact guise might vary,\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EBut my goals and my actions do not.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EAnd even though my most important organ lies\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EQuartered outside of my bodies, the others will stand united by it\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EThrough victory and defeat.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI am...\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-09T18:01:33Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2015 06:01  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Deutherius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Echanged one word\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cantab","CreatedById":104935,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T18:17:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EA pen?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T18:38:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELongshot, but... Mario?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T18:46:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENeither of those I\u0027m afraid.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nemrav","CreatedById":91029,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T20:07:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe doctor...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eits seems that its meant to be a time traveller at least...., tell me if im on track...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T20:16:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nemrav\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Nemrav\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThe doctor...\u003Cp\u003Eits seems that its meant to be a time traveller at least...., tell me if im on track...\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s a nice guess and would fit \u003Cem\u003Esome\u003C/em\u003E of the riddle. I like it! But it\u0027s nowhere near the actual answer \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T20:35:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EA tarot deck? Or perhaps is it a specific card?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T21:09:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EA tarot deck? Or perhaps is it a specific card?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt is not a tarot deck, but you are closer with the second guess. I would like the answer to be very specific, please \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T21:45:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKing of Hearts?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEdit: Ace of Spades?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T21:56:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robotengineer\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Robotengineer\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EKing of Hearts?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECorrect! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Your turn now.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso kudos to Xannari for being so close.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://spiritualnutrition.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/king-of-hearts1-e1311868034327.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022king-of-hearts1-e1311868034327.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAs the supreme authority of this dimension,\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECard images are (for all intents and purposes) 2D, and he is the king - a supreme ruler\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI am the first and the last one of the lot\u003Cp\u003EWhen the mood is solitary,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA rather bad play on the word \u0022Solitaire\u0022, usually a single player card game, where the king has to be the first card laid on the table by the player and the last card to close up a successfuly completed pack\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EMy sword acompanies both of my selves.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe king is usually pictured with a sword in one hand. Most cards are also drawn symmetrically so the card can be held upside down and still be readable - this gives the king two mirrored bodies\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EMy exact guise might vary,\u003Cp\u003EBut my goals and my actions do not.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEvery deck might have different illustrations, but the rules of the game itself (and therefore the king\u0027s actions) don\u0027t change during the game.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAnd even though my most important organ lies\u003Cp\u003EQuartered outside of my bodies,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u0022Heart\u0022 is the only card suit that is also an organ, and it is usually displayed two times next to each king, giving a total count of 4 (it should be \u0022Split in twain\u0022 instead of \u0022Quartered\u0022, but I realised that way too late - sorry)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ethe others will stand united by it\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere are, of course, other cards that follow the king\u0027s suit\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThrough victory and defeat.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe cards will still stay the same regardless of the player winning or losing the game\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI hope it wasn\u0027t too bad \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-09T21:59:02Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2015 09:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Deutherius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T22:13:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy first riddle as well.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EThe final terminal for distant travelers,\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ethey bring joy to those who greet them.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProbably too short/simple, but the only thing I could think up right now.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-10T00:29:51Z\u0022 title=\u002204/10/2015 12:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Robotengineer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ETypos!\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:04:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDiseases?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:12:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EDiseases?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENope, not even close.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:17:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EComputer?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ethanadams","CreatedById":136913,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:21:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAirport terminal ?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:23:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ethanadams\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Ethanadams\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAirport terminal ?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAirport computer...?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:29:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust realized a typo, apologies for any inconvenience. fixed now. Still no correct guesses, hopefully the fix will make it somewhat clearer.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robotengineer\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Robotengineer\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cem\u003EThe final terminal for distant travelers,\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ethey bring joy to those who greet them.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:32:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOr maybe railroads. Then again, you can\u0027t really meet a railroads...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EA gravestone?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T00:58:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022vexx32\u0022 data-cite=\u0022vexx32\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EA gravestone?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EShoot. I think it\u0027s the plural.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eyou can\u0027t really meet a railroads...\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA railroads... Great job, me. Well done. I can grammar.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-10T01:01:29Z\u0022 title=\u002204/10/2015 01:01  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Xannari Ferrows\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T01:26:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENope on all accounts.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cantab","CreatedById":104935,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T02:43:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEyes? Or ears?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T04:04:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Kerbal rendition of the Alcubbierre drive? I think this suffers from a mild case of \u0022everything fits\u0022 syndrome.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robotengineer","CreatedById":104525,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-10T04:04:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cantab\u0022 data-cite=\u0022cantab\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EEyes? Or ears?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EClose, but not quite what I had in mind.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#C0C0C0;\u0022\u003E--updated--\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xannari Ferrows\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThe Kerbal rendition of the Alcubbierre drive? I think this suffers from a mild case of \u0022everything fits\u0022 syndrome.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt might, I only realized a little while after posting how many interpretations it 